  "time_ut": 1656303374,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0b9c\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajid challenges to hold a referendum",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Opposition leader Sajid Premadasa has challenged the government to hold an immediate referendum to form a new government.",
        "He said the United People's Power was ready to accept the responsibility of the country under the new policies that could solve the existing problems.",
        "\"Give the people a chance to hold a referendum immediately. The people of the country will decide the best team to solve the country's problems. We are ready to accept the responsibility of the country"
      ],
